     3	/**
     4	 * A viem extension that adds TEVM actions to a viem client.
     5	 *
     6	 * This function creates a viem extension that adds the full set of TEVM-specific actions to any viem client
     7	 * that has been configured with the TEVM transport. These actions provide direct access to the Ethereum
     8	 * Virtual Machine's capabilities, including:
     9	 *
    10	 * - Low-level EVM execution (`tevmCall`)
    11	 * - Contract interaction with ABI encoding/decoding (`tevmContract`)
    12	 * - Contract deployment (`tevmDeploy`)
